### TeX ###
## Core latex/pdflatex auxiliary files:
*.aux
*.lof
*.log
*.lot
*.fls
*.out
*.toc
*.xdv
*.gz

## Intermediate documents:
*.dvi
*-converted-to.*

### Editor ###
## Vim & Emacs temp files:
.*sw[op]
*~

### Mac OS X ###
## Mac OS X metadata files:
*.DS_Store

### Private ###
## Resume output and job-targeted resumes:
resumes/

### Node ###
## src/present/ assembler + pptx generator deps (installed by install.sh):
node_modules/

### Worktrees ###
## stacking-dev worktrees:
.worktrees/

### Obsidian ###
## Obsidian local workspace state (per-machine, not shareable):
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json
.obsidian/cache
.obsidian/plugins/*/data.json

